{{!
    @template local_dimensions/central/move_competency_modal

    Body of the "move competency to position" modal on the Plans tab: a single select
    listing every position (numbered, annotated with the competency currently there).
    Rendered client-side by local_dimensions/central/plans inside a core/modal_save_cancel;
    the JS reads the selected index on save and issues one reorder web-service call.

    Context variables required:
    * options (array) {value, label, selected} - One entry per list position.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "options": [
            {"value": 0, "label": "1. Communication", "selected": true},
            {"value": 1, "label": "2. Teamwork", "selected": false}
        ]
    }
}}
<div class="local-dimensions-central-plans-move">
    <label class="d-block small text-muted mb-1" for="local-dimensions-plans-move-position">
        {{#str}}central_plans_moveto_label, local_dimensions{{/str}}
    </label>
    <select class="form-select" id="local-dimensions-plans-move-position" name="local-dimensions-plans-move-position">
        {{#options}}
        <option value="{{value}}"{{#selected}} selected{{/selected}}>{{label}}</option>
        {{/options}}
    </select>
</div>
